## Agent Roster

23 custom agents at `~/.claude/agents/`. Use them proactively — don't wait to be asked.

### Core Agents
| Agent | Model | When to use |
|---|---|---|
| `planner` | sonnet (blue) | Starting any new feature, refactor, or complex change |
| `debugger` | sonnet (red) | Any error, test failure, or unexpected behavior |
| `test-writer` | sonnet (green) | After writing or modifying code; when coverage is needed |
| `code-reviewer` | haiku (cyan) | Immediately after writing or modifying code |
| `data-scientist` | sonnet (orange) | Data analysis tasks, SQL queries, BigQuery exploration |
| `db-reader` | haiku (purple) | Read-only DB queries (SELECT only — writes blocked at hook level) |
| `commit` | haiku (yellow) | Creating semantic git commits |
| `security` | sonnet (magenta) | Security review, OWASP, secrets scanning |

